    <string name="action_send_feedback_email">Send feedback by email</string>
    <string name="feedback_email_subject">Dotlist Feedback</string>
    <string name="faq_q1">How do I share a list?</string>
    <string name="faq_a1">Open the list, tap the share icon and copy the invite code. The other person enters it under \"My lists\" when joining.</string>
    <string name="faq_q2">What\'s the difference between owner, admin, and editor?</string>
    <string name="faq_a2">The owner created a list and can delete it or transfer ownership. Admins can additionally share the invite code and manage members. Editors can view and edit tasks, but can\'t manage members.</string>
    <string name="faq_q3">Why do I lose access when I reinstall the app?</string>
    <string name="faq_a3">Without a linked Google account, your access is only stored on this device. Link your Google account under \"Manage account\" to prevent this.</string>
    <string name="faq_q4">Do I get notifications when the app is closed?</string>
    <string name="faq_a4">Yes, as long as the app is still running in the background. If the app is fully terminated, notifications may be delayed or not arrive at all.</string>

